        %a{:href => "http://www.meetup.com/swmobile", :target => "_blank"} SWmobile meetup group
    %p With over 140 members, the group meets every 6-8 weeks to discuss mobile design and development. Currently Bristol-based, there are plans to expand the group to further afield in the South West.
